room_title: Escape room "Chaos in the Galleria" by Omescape in San Jose
room_description: Following the theft of the worldâ€™s 5th largest diamond, two amateur thieves have enlisted you in helping them recover the stolen gem, which they left behind while making their escape through the famous Galleria Mall. Known for its variety of retail and leisure businesses, the Galleria Mall has become the only obstacle between you and a once in a lifetime payday. Can your team rise to the occasion and escape with the diamond or will you be caught and tried as accomplices in what would be the greatest diamond heist in history?
